OL,3,CVisitor bookings down 20% this summer
OL,4,Cafter poor weather
OL,6,FAccommodation bookings have fallen 20%
OL,7,Facross the West Country this summer
OL,8,Fcompared to last year, according to
OL,9,Fone of the region's largest tourism
OL,10,Fboards.
OL,12,FVisit Somerset say that the downturn
OL,13,Fin spend has led to #120 million in
OL,14,Flost revenue in the county alone.
OL,16,FAs well as the cost of living crisis,
OL,17,Ftourism bosses blame the poor weather,
OL,18,Fand technology which allows people to
OL,19,Fleave bookings until the last minute.
