OL,3,CVisitor bookings down 20% this summer
OL,4,Cafter poor weather
OL,6,F"It hasn't been a good summer weather
OL,7,Fwise, or a good year," says John
OL,8,FTurner, CEO of Visit Somerset.
OL,10,F"We're hearing reports that people -
OL,11,Fbecause it's so cheap to fly abroad -
OL,12,Fare going abroad where they'll get
OL,13,Fguaranteed sunshine. Because we have
OL,14,Fthe ability on our mobile phones to
OL,15,Fbook very very quickly, it means that
OL,16,Fpeople can make snap decisions very
OL,17,Fvery quickly."
