OL,3,CVisitor bookings down 20% this summer
OL,4,Cafter poor weather
OL,6,FBut although those issues may be
OL,7,Fdeterring British visitors,
OL,8,Finternational visitors are still
OL,9,Fcoming in very large numbers.
OL,11,FAttractions in Bath like the Jane
OL,12,FAusten Centre have seen the proportion
OL,13,Fof foreign visitors continue to grow
OL,14,Fsince the end of Covid restrictions,
OL,15,Fespecially Americans.
OL,17,FThe Centre, which was threatened with
OL,18,Fclosure during the pandemic, saw a
OL,19,Frecord 200,000 visitors last year and
OL,20,Fis on course to hit the same figure
OL,21,Fthis year.
