OL,3,CVisitor bookings down 20% this summer
OL,4,Cafter poor weather
OL,6,FIt's a similar story at the Roman
OL,7,FBaths, who have seen a 5% upturn in
OL,8,Fvisitor numbers this summer, with the
OL,9,Fincrease mainly international.
OL,10,FManagers would like to raise the
OL,11,Fproportion of domestic visitors.
OL,13,F"We've got people coming to the Roman
OL,14,FBaths from all over the world. But
OL,15,Fwe'd really like to see as many people
OL,16,Ffrom the local area come as well."
OL,17,Fsays Robert Campbell from Bath and
OL,18,FNorth East Somerset Council.
OL,20,FResidents of Bath and North East
OL,21,FSomerset get free entry to the Baths.
